根據2013年10月的統計，史丹福大學總共錄取了7,601位[[本科|本科生]]及11,075位[[研究生|研究生]]，<ref name="CDS"/>女性佔了本科群組的47%及專業及研究生人口的41%，同年度的新生保留率達99%。<ref name="CDS"/>

其在2011-12學年則賦予了1,715個本科、2,278碩士、764博士及366個專業學位證明。<ref name="CDS"/>而2011年的四年本科生畢業率為76%，六年的則有96%。<ref name="CDS"/>四年的畢業率較低是因為大學開辦了學士碩士連讀課程，允許本科生進一步取得2年的碩士文憑作為他們本科學習的一個延續。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/college/highest-grad-rate |title=Best Colleges—Education—US News and World Report |publisher=Colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com |date=2009-08-19 |accessdate=2010-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090314054424/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/college/highest-grad-rate |archivedate=2009-03-14 }}</ref>

2010年的本科生中，有15%為在史丹福就讀的第一代學生（即沒有任何家屬親戚就讀大学之背景）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |url=http://www.stanforddaily.com/2010/10/01/concerns-of-first-generation-students-must-remain-a-priority/ |title=Concerns of first-generation students must remain a priority |date=2010-10-01 |work=The Stanford Daily |accessdate=2011-01-31 |archive-date=2021-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223025538/https://www.stanforddaily.com/2010/10/01/concerns-of-first-generation-students-must-remain-a-priority/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===學生住宿===
所有的史丹福一年級生均需留校住宿，他們亦獲得未來四年的宿位保證。<ref name="CDS"/><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=https://www.stanford.edu/dept/rde/cgi-bin/drupal/housing/apply/apply-housing |title=Stanford University—Student Housing—Apply for Housing 2013-14 |publisher=Stanford.edu |date= |accessdate=2014-02-02 |archive-date=2014-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140605195815/http://www.stanford.edu/dept/rde/cgi-bin/drupal/housing/apply/apply-housing |dead-url=no }}</ref>當中有89%的本科生獲分配校園內的宿位。根據史丹福房屋分配辦公室提供的資料，校方為這些住宿學生提供了80種的住宿形式，包括宿舍、合作社、聯排式住宅、兄弟和姊妹會等。<ref name="ugradres">{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.stanford.edu/dept/resed/Residences/ |title=Stanford Housing—Undergraduate Residences |publisher=Stanford University |accessdate=2008-11-27 |archive-date=2012-12-15 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20121215043129/http://www.stanford.edu/dept/resed/Residences/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在1969-1991年期間，學校提供了118所流動房屋作為“臨時宿舍”，這些地點現已成為了卡斯塔諾、金博爾及馬纓丹宿舍的所在地。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.stanford.edu/pr/91/910724Arc1246.html |title=Manzanita trailers to house Webb Ranch workers |publisher=News.stanford.edu |date= |accessdate=2010-07-09 |archive-date=2010-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100729084308/http://news.stanford.edu/pr/91/910724Arc1246.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>大部分的住宿房屋均在校園本部附近，距離大部分的圖書館及課室只有10分鐘的步行（或踏自行車）距離。有些只提供給新生，有些只給大二的學生，有些只給高年級生，而剩下的則不限學生類別。大部分的宿舍為男女共用，而兄弟會的社房只供男性居住；同樣地，姊妹會的則只接納女性學生（但羅斯舍堂為唯一非姊妹會的女性宿舍）。這當中絕大部分的宿舍不限男女的居住樓層，但亦有一部分為單性樓層建設，即男女隔層居住（這包括除阿羅約及岡田等所有威爾伯宿舍）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.stanford.edu/dept/rde/shs/ugrad/wilbur.htm#junipero |title=Stanford University—Student Housing—Tour Undergraduate Housing |publisher=Stanford.edu |date= |accessdate=2010-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110514044724/http://www.stanford.edu/dept/rde/shs/ugrad/wilbur.htm#junipero |archivedate=2011-05-14 }}</ref>自2009-10年起，史丹福房屋計劃組就預計，所有要求居住全新生宿舍的學生都能獲得滿足。有關部門亦稱，將會有近三分之二的新生入住斯托及威爾伯宿舍，剩下三分之一要求住在其他類別的宿舍的學生，會入住佛羅倫薩·摩爾等其他舍堂。<ref name="froshhousing">{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://parents.stanford.edu/newsletter/09fall/golder.html |title=Parents' Newsletter, Fall 2009—Golder looks to improve life and learning in the residences |publisher=Stanford University |accessdate=2009-09-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100705165210/http://parents.stanford.edu/newsletter/09fall/golder.html |archivedate=2010-07-05 }}</ref>史丹福的新男女同室居住計劃於2008年亮相。這是應全體學生一致的取向及其他同類學府（如[[衛斯理大學|衛斯理]]、[[克拉克大學|克拉克]]、[[達特茅斯學院|達特茅斯]]、[[布朗大學|布朗]]、[[賓夕法尼亞大學|賓夕法尼亞]]及[[歐柏林學院|歐柏林]]）的做法而下的決策。<ref name="genderblind">{{en}}{{cite news |url=http://daily.stanford.edu/article/2008/4/8/genderneutralHousingPlanUnveiled |title=Gender-neutral housing plan unveiled |work=Stanford Daily |date=2008-04-08 |accessdate=2008-11-27 |last=Xu |first=Joanna |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080621003855/http://daily.stanford.edu/article/2008/4/8/genderneutralHousingPlanUnveiled |archivedate=2008-06-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

史丹福有很多特色住宿房屋。包括：按照修讀課程的類別招納學生的“主題房舍”，<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.stanford.edu/dept/resed/Residences/ |title=Stanford Undergraduate Residences |publisher=Stanford University |accessdate=2009-12-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121215043129/http://www.stanford.edu/dept/resed/Residences/ |archivedate=2012-12-15 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.stanford.edu/group/themed/coops/columbae.html |title=Columbae House |publisher=Stanford University |accessdate=2012-04-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120411152235/http://www.stanford.edu/group/themed/coops/columbae.html |archivedate=2012-04-11 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.stanford.edu/group/synergy/ |title=Synergy House |publisher=Stanford University |accessdate=2012-04-10 |archive-date=2014-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102124254/http://www.stanford.edu/group/synergy// |dead-url=no }}</ref>及要求社員為日常起居飲食共同作出貢獻的合作社堂。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.stanford.edu/group/resed/cgi-bin/row/terra/drupal/|title=About Terra|work=ResEd|publisher=Stanford University|accessdate=2013-08-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110153701/http://www.stanford.edu/group/resed/cgi-bin/row/terra/drupal/|archivedate=2013-11-10}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.stanford.edu/dept/resed/Staff/StaffResources/StudentMgmt/CoOps.html |title=Residential Education—Cooperative Houses |publisher=Stanford University |accessdate=2008-11-27 |archive-date=2009-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090526032501/http://www.stanford.edu/dept/resed/Staff/StaffResources/StudentMgmt/CoOps.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===體育競賽===
主條目：{{link-en|史丹福樞機紅|Stanford Cardinal}}
[[File:Stanstadium_view.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:11-04-06-LSJUMB-003.jpg|thumb]]

史丹福目前共有36支體育競賽代表隊（18支女子、15支男子及1支男女隊）、19支學會體育隊及37支校內體育競賽隊伍。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.stanford.edu/dept/pe/cgi-bin/cardinalrec/clubsports/|title=Stanford Cardinal Recreation - Club Sports|publisher=Stanford University|accessdate=2014-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110014310/http://www.stanford.edu/dept/pe/cgi-bin/cardinalrec/clubsports/|archive-date=2014-01-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>共有大約800名學生參與其中，校方亦提供300個體育獎學金計劃。其體育團隊正式名稱為“史丹福樞機紅”，意指[[樞機紅|樞機紅色]]而非紅雀。此稱謂始於1930年，當時舊有的稱號“印第安人”因受到美洲本土裔學生以宗族歧視的理由而遭棄用。大學為太平洋十二校聯盟及{{link-en|太平洋高山體育聯盟|Mountain Pacific Sports Federation}}的成員，參與全美大學體育協會甲組的賽事。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.norpacfieldhockey.com/ |title=NorPac |publisher=i2i Interactive |year=2007 |accessdate=2007-06-08 |archive-date=2007-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070617134534/http://www.norpacfieldhockey.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

史丹福最大的體育競爭對手，為位處北部東灣的[[伯克萊加州大學|柏克萊加大]]，此關係亦為兩校的傳統之一。每屆“大比賽（{{lang|en|Big Game}}）”的優勝者有權持有“史丹福之斧”錦標。此美式足球比賽最初於1892年3月19日假[[三藩市|三藩市]]海特街公園進行。在八千名觀眾的注目下，史丹福以14比10贏得是次賽事。其也在1902年，首度參與[[玫瑰碗|玫瑰碗]]競賽。可是，參賽者引發的暴力事件及賽事結束後的觀眾騷亂，使三藩市政府在1905年正式禁止該市以後任何“大比賽”的舉辦，而史丹福校方亦於次年禁止一切的足球賽事。1906–1914年的“大比賽”以橄欖球的形式舉行。不過，足球賽事最後還是因比賽模式的改良而在1919年獲得了復辦。<ref name="Starr3">{{en}}{{cite book|last=Starr|first=Kevin|title=Americans and the California Dream|url=https://archive.org/details/americanscalifor00star|publisher=Oxford University Press|location=Oxford|year=1973|pages=[https://archive.org/details/americanscalifor00star/page/336 336]–338|chapter=Life Among the Best and Truest: David Starr Jordan and the Founding of Stanford University |isbn=0-19-501644-0}}</ref>

史丹福於1976–77年起，每一年都會奪得至少一個全美大學體育協會賽事的冠軍，<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/sports/college/2010-06-22-stanford-directors-cup_N.htm|title=USA Today|date=2010-06-22|accessdate=2014-02-10|archive-date=2012-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120313111640/http://www.usatoday.com/sports/college/2010-06-22-stanford-directors-cup_N.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>並自創立以來，贏得合共104次的國家隊冠軍（為全國高校第二佳績，僅次於[[加州大學洛杉磯分校|洛杉磯加大]]），及467次國家個人冠軍（全國大學之冠）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://champions.stanford.edu/history/individual-national-champions/|title=Stanford – Home of Champions|publisher=Champions.stanford.edu.|accessdate=2013-07-15|archive-date=2014-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140404153219/http://champions.stanford.edu/history/individual-national-champions/|dead-url=no}}</ref>其亦連續17年為全國大學體育競技董事杯的年度得主。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.nacda.com/directorscup/nacda-directorscup-previous-scoring.html |title=NACDA Official Athletic Site - Directors Cup |publisher=CBSSports.com College Network |date= |accessdate=2013-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110102202358/http://www.nacda.com/directorscup/nacda-directorscup-previous-scoring.html |archive-date=2011-01-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://champions.stanford.edu/history/by-the-numbers/ |title=Stanford Athletics 'By The Numbers' : Stanford - Home of Champions |publisher=Stanford.edu |date= |accessdate=2013-12-20 |archive-date=2011-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110508174901/http://champions.stanford.edu/history/by-the-numbers |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://facts.stanford.edu/campuslife/athletics |title=Cardinal Athletics: Stanford University Facts |publisher=Stanford.edu |date= |accessdate=2013-12-20 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225015012/https://facts.stanford.edu/campuslife/athletics/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>史丹福代表隊在1912年起，於每屆的[[奧林匹克運動會|奧林匹克運動會]]都有取得獎牌，目前已經累積到244枚，當中包括129枚金牌。在[[2008年夏季奧林匹克運動會|2008北京奧運會]]中，史丹福更為全美表現最佳的高校體育隊伍。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title=What Stanford University and Japan have in Common|url=http://www.freakonomics.com/2008/09/03/what-japan-and-stanford-university-have-in-common/|publisher=Freakonomics|access-date=2014-02-10|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226003806/https://freakonomics.com/2008/09/03/what-japan-and-stanford-university-have-in-common/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=Stanford Athletes Complete Olympic Action |url=http://www.gostanford.com/sports/olympics/spec-rel/081412aab.html |publisher=Stanford Athletics |accessdate=2013-11-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130521144911/http://www.gostanford.com/sports/olympics/spec-rel/081412aab.html |archivedate=2013-05-21 }}</ref>自2004年起，史丹福也累積取得了182面夏季奧運會獎牌，當中的12金、2銀、2銅是在最近的2012年比賽中奪得。<ref name="olympics12">{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.gostanford.com/sports/olympics/spec-rel/081412aab.html |title=Stanford Athletes Complete Olympic Action |publisher=Stanford Daily |accessdate=2014-02-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130521144911/http://www.gostanford.com/sports/olympics/spec-rel/081412aab.html |archivedate=2013-05-21 }}</ref>

